    bibo:volume "3852" ;
    dc:creator "Ale-Rocha, Rosaly; Freitas-Silva, Rafael Augusto Pinheiro De" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "New species of Oropezella Collin (Diptera, Hybotidae, Ocydromiinae) from Brazil and Costa Rica, with comments on the relationships among species-groups" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229703> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229703>
    dc:description "FIGURES 101 – 108. Oropezella undulata. Hypopygium: 101, ventral aspect; 102, dorsal aspect; 103, phallus, lateral aspect (hypandrium spotted); 104, 105, left and right epandrial lamella, surstylus and cercus, respectively, lateral aspect. Female terminalia: 106, dorsal aspect; 107, ventral aspect; 108, lateral aspect. Scale bar: hypopygium = 0.1 mm; female terminalia = 0.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229703/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

